quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  21,42,"Say, “Who can keep you safe by night and by day from God, the Merciful Benefactor?” Yet they turn away from the mention of their Guardian Evolver"
  21,43,"Or have they gods that can guard them from Us? They have no power to aid themselves, nor can they be defended from Us"
  21,44,"No, We gave the good things of this life to these people and their fathers, until the period grew long for them. Do they not see that We gradually reduce the land in their control from its outlying borders? Is it then they who will win"
  21,45,"Say, “I only warn you according to revelation.” But the deaf will not hear the call when they are warned"
  21,46,"If even a gust of the punishment of your Lord reaches them, they will then say, “Woe to us, we did wrong indeed.”"
  21,47,"We will set up scales of justice for the Day of Accountability, so no soul will be dealt with unjustly in the least. And if there be the weight of a mustard seed, We will bring it to account, and enough are We to take account"
  21,48,"In the past, We granted to Moses and Aaron the Criterion, and a light, and a message for those who are conscious"
  21,49,"Those who are conscious of their Guardian Evolver in their most private thoughts, and who hold the Hour in awe"
  21,50,And this is a blessed message that We have sent down. Will you then reject it